title: ABNKKBSNPLAko?! The Movie
description:
ABNKKBSNPLAko?! is a 2001 novel by Filipino author Bob Ong Ã¢â‚¬â€ his first and most popular work. The title is meant to be read phonetically as "Aba, nakakabasa na pala ako?!", which can be roughly translated as "Wow, I can read now?!" The novel details what are supposedly the childhood memories of the author, from his earliest days as a student until his first few years at work.

A film version titled ABNKKBSNPLAko?! The Movie was released on 19 February 2014. It stars Meg Imperial as Portia and Jericho Rosales as Bob Ong, and was directed by Mark Meily. The script was written by Ned Trespasses
